BR_text.BRsummary: Missing best config after fit for object detection fit example
BR_text.BRdescription:
After executing object detection example, it only produces:
 <denchmark-code>INFO:autogluon.task.object_detection.object_detection:>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>> finish model fitting
 INFO:autogluon.task.object_detection.object_detection:The best config:
 </denchmark-code>
 
 while no best config is reported.
 Might relate to <denchmark-link:https://github.com/awslabs/autogluon/issues/29>#29</denchmark-link>

comments_0.comment_text:
Thanks for catching that. have fixed it in a new PR <denchmark-link:https://github.com/awslabs/autogluon/pull/126>#126</denchmark-link>
